tools.description:
Retrieve the system-configured minimum and maximum allowable spending limits.

Returns:
    dict: {
        "success": True,
        "data": {
            "min_limit": float,
            "max_limit": float
        }
    }
    or
    {
        "success": False,
        "error": str
    }

Constraints:
    - Must return the system-wide spending limit bounds if set.
    - If not set, returns sensible defaults (min: 0.0, max: 10000.0).
